From 0463a37586aceebd09c1c294446d0c3b15a5fc4b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Thomas Guillem <thomas@gllm.fr>
Date: Fri, 4 Jul 2025 13:24:26 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] core: load packetizers by type

Check less modules when loading a packetizer and ensure the
audio/video/spu union in es_format_t is correctly initialized for a
given category.
